The following events took place in '''4800 [[Galactic Standard Calendar|BBY]]'''.

==Events==
*The [[Spice/Legends|spice]] [[Ryll/Legends|ryll]] was discovered on [[Ryloth/Legends|Ryloth]]. {{Circa}}<ref name="NEC" />
*The [[Gank Massacres]] began when the newly-discovered [[Porporite]] species were whipped into a homicidal frenzy by ryll. Various factions of the [[Neimoidian/Legends|Neimoidian]] species hired [[Mercenary/Legends|mercenaries]] from the [[Gank/Legends|Gank]] species to protect them, but the Gank exterminated the Porporites and went on a violent rampage of their own.<ref name="NEC" />

